服务：很到位特别热情，尤其是入住办理的美女Grihan女士服务特别满意??给个大赞', '2025-02-22', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'', ''卫生状况'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235n12000io0lang3303_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233312000inzp89r3509_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233e12000inz5s05EA44_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '房间很好，整洁。去那里都很方便，交通便捷，对面就是广州酒家。服务很到位，好多个餐', '房间很好，整洁。去那里都很方便，交通便捷，对面就是广州酒家。服务很到位，好多个餐厅，吃饭很方便。各式的服务人员，各司其职，办理入住和退房，基本不用等等待。', '2025-01-27', 5, '[''交通便利性'', ''周边配套'', ''退房/入住效率'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235012000i3ohjqdF122_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236b12000i3og49c1338_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236n12000i3ozui92CD7_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232w12000i3ochej0BC1_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230v12000i3o83920A0E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '卫生：酒店卫生干净，尤其房间卫生做的十分好', '卫生：酒店卫生干净，尤其房间卫生做的十分好
